  "translations": {
    "en": "So the believer says to the image: May Allah have mercy on you, what an excellent companion! You came out with me from my grave, you have not ceased giving me glad tidings of delight and honor from Allah, Mighty and Majestic, until that was so. So who are you? The image says: I am the delight that you brought upon your believing brother in the world. Allah created me from it to give you glad tidings.",
